{"tid":453053,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"因 Kevin Spacey 性穌擾指控, Netflix cut 咗 House of Cards","createTime":"2017-10-30T23:51:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T11:48:23.000Z","uid":130105,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e72d25ad410169a1f1961f4599f2b524054c582b","tid":453053,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T23:51:51.000Z","msg":"好快手<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Netflix cancels House of Cards and says they are 'deeply troubled' by Kevin Spacey sex assault claims while gay stars SLAM actor including Rosie O'Donnell - who says 'we all knew about u'</span><br />\n <br />\n&bull;Netflix has revealed that the upcoming sixth season of 'House of Cards,' which is in production now, will be its last  <br />\n&bull;This comes after 'Rent' star Anthony Rapp gave an interview claiming that a then-26-year-old Spacey tried to sexually assault him when he was 14 in 1986<br />\n&bull;Spacey responded to that allegation with a rambling statement in which he said he did not recall the incident, apologized to Rapp and then came out as gay<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/10/30/19/45D326BD00000578-5032947-image-a-73_1509392267264.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F19%2F45D326BD00000578-5032947-image-a-73_1509392267264.jpg&h=de149a24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNetflix has revealed that the upcoming sixth season of 'House of Cards,' which is in production now, will be its last (Spacey and Robin Wright in House of Cards above)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/10/30/22/45D76A0C00000578-5032947-Speaking_out_and_proud_Rosie_O_Donnell_above_in_October_was_one_-a-111_1509401168105.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F22%2F45D76A0C00000578-5032947-Speaking_out_and_proud_Rosie_O_Donnell_above_in_October_was_one_-a-111_1509401168105.jpg&h=d65f78be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSpeaking out and proud: Rosie O'Donnell (above in October) was one of the first to go after Spacey on social media after he said he did not remember his attempts to sexually assault a then-teenage Anthony Rapp<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/10/30/22/45D80D9900000578-5032947-image-a-110_1509401168099.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F22%2F45D80D9900000578-5032947-image-a-110_1509401168099.jpg&h=8e289e54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Wanda Sykes<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/10/30/20/45D76A2000000578-5032947-image-a-88_1509394765735.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F20%2F45D76A2000000578-5032947-image-a-88_1509394765735.jpg&h=f65d26c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Not mincing words: 'u don't remember the incident - 30 years ago? - f*** u kevin - like Harvey [Weinstein] we all knew about u - I hope more men come forward,' said Rosie (above)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/10/30/21/45D7F20F00000578-5032947-image-a-107_1509400091613.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F21%2F45D7F20F00000578-5032947-image-a-107_1509400091613.jpg&h=09371eda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Not having it: Wanda Sykes tweeted: 'No no no no no! You do not get to &quot;choose&quot; to hide under the rainbow! Kick rocks!' (above)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/10/30/20/45D2AAB400000578-5032947-image-m-94_1509395002114.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F20%2F45D2AAB400000578-5032947-image-m-94_1509395002114.jpg&h=43ce9ddb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n La Vie Boheme: Rapp (above with Idina Menzel in the 2005 film version of 'Rent') shot to fame as a member of the original Broadway cast <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/10/30/20/45D76A1900000578-5032947-image-a-85_1509394680343.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F20%2F45D76A1900000578-5032947-image-a-85_1509394680343.jpg&h=931ffbb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n No love lost: 'I am sorry that Kevin only saw fit to acknowledge his truth when he though it would serve him &iquest; just as his denial served him for so many years,' said Quinto (above with Spacey at the 2011 Berlin Film Festival) <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/10/30/20/45D6EA5600000578-5032947-The_victim_May_Anthony_Rapp_s_voice_be_the_one_which_is_amplifie-m-91_1509394927933.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F20%2F45D6EA5600000578-5032947-The_victim_May_Anthony_Rapp_s_voice_be_the_one_which_is_amplifie-m-91_1509394927933.jpg&h=eb61702a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n The victim: 'May Anthony Rapp&iquest;s voice be the one which is amplified here. Victim&iquest;s voices are the ones that deserve to be heard,' wrote Quinto in his statement (above)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/10/30/20/45D4F64100000578-5032947-image-m-105_1509396446520.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F20%2F45D4F64100000578-5032947-image-m-105_1509396446520.jpg&h=69c0a31c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Boy: Rapp in 1986 at the age of 14 (top left), when the alleged incident occurred at Spacey's apartment<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/10/30/19/45D43C6E00000578-5032947-image-m-79_1509393414991.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F19%2F45D43C6E00000578-5032947-image-m-79_1509393414991.jpg&h=ee0da53f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/10/30/20/45D765DE00000578-5032947-image-a-90_1509394896384.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F20%2F45D765DE00000578-5032947-image-a-90_1509394896384.jpg&h=6e5ff81d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/10/30/19/45D43C7600000578-5032947-image-m-78_1509393402134.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F19%2F45D43C7600000578-5032947-image-m-78_1509393402134.jpg&h=f759f4a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/10/30/20/45D78E8500000578-5032947-image-m-96_1509395517402.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F20%2F45D78E8500000578-5032947-image-m-96_1509395517402.jpg&h=47a3b50e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/10/30/20/45D7A08C00000578-5032947-image-a-97_1509396286788.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F20%2F45D7A08C00000578-5032947-image-a-97_1509396286788.jpg&h=880e062a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/10/30/21/45D39AF800000578-5032947-image-a-108_1509400100815.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F21%2F45D39AF800000578-5032947-image-a-108_1509400100815.jpg&h=15bbc2cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nKevin Spacey has apologised over sexual advance claim.<br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5032947/House-Cards-cancelled-Kevin-Spacey-attack.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-5032947%2FHouse-Cards-cancelled-Kevin-Spacey-attack.html&d=en1O0unu1ryP%2FPqfndsG5CwN6